column10: I was traveling southbound on Crystal Drive when a Ride Share driver stopped and pulled into the bike lane to pick up a passenger causing me to slam on the breaks. Additionally, cars traveling behind the ride share were impacted and harassed the driver enough that they moved out of the lane into a emergency vehicle spot.
